import React from 'react'

import {Container,Row,Col} from 'react-bootstrap'
const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <footer>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col className='text-center py-3'>
                        Grupo Empresarial Kd
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
         
            
        </footer>
    )
} 

export default Footer
